                "name": "Acid Spit",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A chon chon can spit a disgusting blob of acid at a single foe, making a ranged attack with a range of 30 feet and no range increment. A successful attack deals 2d4 points of acid damage and forces the target to make a DC 13 Fortitude saving throw to avoid becoming nauseated for 1 round. The save DC is Constitution-based."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
