                "name": "Jabber",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A chon chon swarm mutters even more loudly than a solitary chon chon. Any creature attempting to cast a spell within 30 feet of a chon chon must make a successful DC 11 concentration check or lose the spell. This is a sonic, mindaffecting effect. The concentration DC is Charisma-based."
